<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.8.1">
<l>intira ṉōṭu piramaṉ īca ṉimaiya varellām</l>
<l>mantira māmalar koṇṭu maṟaintuva rāyvantu niṉṟār</l>
<l>cantiraṉ māḷikai cērum catirarkaḷ veḷḷaṟai niṉṟā</l>
<l>yantiyam pōtitu vākum aḻakaṉē kāppiṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Brahmā, Īśa, and all the [other] celestials,</l>
<l rend="indent">along with Indra</l>
<l>came, bringing the great flowers</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] mantras and stood hidden nearby.</l>
<l>You who stands in Veḷḷaṟai where clever men</l>
<l rend="indent">are gathered in mansions [touched] by the moon!</l>
<l>Beauty! It is the beautiful time of twilight,</l>
<l rend="indent">come so that [I can] fasten a kāppu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
